The end of slavery
Firez, fearing the arrival of Canian, decides to lead his Joon slaves from the mountain prison to his castle. Capturing the escorts is a real chance to free Kira's family.
#subobj 1
Capture the escort
The escort will be moving from the mountain prison to the city. Your best bet is to intercept it at an intersection in the center of the area.
#subobj 2
Free the slaves
You need to defeat all the guards. The Joons are unarmed and will not be able to help their saviors.
#subobj 3
Escort the Joons to safety
The Two Rivers area is now under Canian control, so that's where you need to repatriate the rescued Joons.
#subobj 4
All the Joons must survive